nodes.text: Nibiru was a forest world, which also boasted at least one large lake. It was located in the Outer Rim's Kakani sector.
During the Galactic Civil War, Princess Leia crash-landed on Nibiru, which prompted the mission to Nibiru.
"Nibiru", or "Planet X", is a planetary object which certain groups claim will collide with or nearly miss the Earth in the early 21st century.
